title: Seahawks WR Jaxon Smith-Njigba named NFL Offensive Player of the Year

sources.title: Seahawks WR Jaxon Smith-Njigba named NFL Offensive Player of the Year
sources.description: Jaxon Smith-Njigba is coming off the best statistical receiving season in Seahawks franchise history and joins Shaun Alexander as Seahawks' OPOY nod.
